OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1781028676
OL,3,CSellafield nuclear workers set to
OL,4,Cstrike once more
OL,6,FA trade union says nearly 2,000
OL,7,Fconstruction workers at Sellafield are
OL,8,Fset to walk out next week in a dispute
OL,9,Fover pay.
OL,11,FSubcontractors, who are members of the
OL,12,FUnite Union at the complex will hold
OL,13,Fstrike from Monday 15 June 2026 until
OL,14,FSunday 21 June 2026.
OL,16,FThe union are calling for a site-
OL,17,Fspecific allowance due to the
OL,18,F"specialist skills needed to work at a
OL,19,Fnuclear site."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/4
