SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1781028676
OL,3,CSellafield nuclear workers set to
OL,4,Cstrike once more
OL,6,FUnite regional officer Ryan Armstrong
OL,7,Fadded: "This is a dispute of the
OL,8,Femployers' own making. Unite remains
OL,9,Fwilling to enter into meaningful
OL,10,Fnegotiations and the site negotiating
OL,11,Fteam continues to work tirelessly to
OL,12,Ffind a resolution.
OL,14,F"We have requested discussions so
OL,15,Fevery opportunity to avoid industrial
OL,16,Faction can be explored. Our members
OL,17,Fsimply want fair recognition for the
OL,18,Fwork they undertake and have been left
OL,19,Fincreasingly frustrated by the
OL,20,Fcontinued failure to engage in
OL,21,Fmeaningful discussions."
OL,26,@oD@HOUvD@AOU}D@XO]
