OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1781028676
OL,3,CSellafield nuclear workers set to
OL,4,Cstrike once more
OL,6,FWorkers previously walked out last
OL,7,FOctober over pay.
OL,9,FA Sellafield Ltd spokesman said: "The
OL,10,Findustrial action taking place at
OL,11,FSellafield is the result of a pay
OL,12,Fdispute between some Unite union
OL,13,Fmembers and their employers.
OL,15,F"As the people involved are not
OL,16,Femployed by Sellafield Ltd this is not
OL,17,Fa dispute that we can resolve.
OL,19,F"Our priority, as always, is to
OL,20,Fmaintain the safety and security of
OL,21,Fthe Sellafield site."
OL,26,@qD@bOUwD@AOU{D@AOU}D@UO]
